members.member: Simple example code to create XML from objects and objects from response XML

This method does a simple Http post to the URI indicated This URI should be pointing at the Litle test system, a host and port will be provided by the Litle Implementations team we'll need to configure access for your organization since the Litle test system is protected by firewalls
Also note that communications to the Litle system will utilize HTTPS for secure transmission of data
Error handling is omitted for this simple example However communication errors are something that should be handled according to your needs
